  dialogueLines:
  - Aaah~ Another adoring fan, I see! Welcome, welcome~
  - You can leave your gifts and flowers anywhere you wish~
  - Uh-
  - " I don\u2019t have-"
  - ' You can watch me as I practise and cheer for me~ '
  - " I\u2019M NOT HERE FOR YOU, I\u2019M HERE FOR TAIKA!!! I NEED YOUR KEY TO GET
    INTO THAT STUPID TENT!"
  - ....W H A T?! THAT NEWCOMER, THE LITTLE TWERP WHO THINKS THEY CAN OUTSHINE ME?! 
    I AM THE TRUE STAR OF THE SHOW, PEOPLE COME FROM MILES AROUND JUST TO SEE MY
    DANCE!
  - ' I will show you! Get ready, child, for you are about to be amazed by the Prima
    Donna herself!'
  - I thought your name is Colombina
  - SHUT UP!!
